D_f(A)=\lim_{t \to 0} \frac{f(A+tA)-f(A)}{t} = \lim_{t \to 0} \frac{(A+tA)^2-A^2}{t} = \lim_{t \to 0} \frac{A^2+AtA+tAA+t^2A^2-A^2}{t}=\lim_{t \to 0} \frac{2tA^2+t^2A^2}{t} =\lim_{t \to 0} 2A^2+tA^2 =2A^2
D_f(A)=2A^2
